des: Welcome to the world of O! With the O, The Oprah Magazine skill! You’ll be inspired, surprised, and delighted every day by our first feature “O to Go,” Oprah’s reading of her bestselling book “What I Know for Sure”, a collection of intimate pieces from her monthly magazine column. We’ll be adding new features soon, so make sure to check in every day. Just say, “Alexa, Ask Oprah Magazine for my O to Go”—and enjoy!
